{"tid":1565193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢發到用曬銀彈，希望有人可以支援下我","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:52.000Z","uid":28252,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3570decfad7a7fd02c44f5c9ef3cd907d5adfb40","tid":1565193,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"由69開始就出黎，616已經辭左職疊埋心水長期online發夢，已經三個月，加上住到好遠嘅我來回出一次黎都要五十幾蚊，真係未到洗曬我都唔想做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟廿二家貧，但唔想兩老擔心就同佢地講自己發夢但夠錢駛，所以希望有心人可以俾到幾百蚊我做下生活費，過埋呢關就求其搵份工捱到出糧先<br />\n<br />\n祝大家最後可以係煲底除罩相見<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLKRN1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLKRN1D.jpg&h=1696aa59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMea3Si.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMea3Si.png&h=2b5f60c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36011737da96c068ef33bfcaa91605a655a2e5f0","tid":1565193,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7fa9d6b3f6168c47aeb013c8ae9653fd94865eff","tid":1565193,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n黃大仙廣場 ，摩士公園<br />\n觀塘海濱公園<br />\n油塘道遊樂場<br />\n2100 紅磡碼頭<br />\n2150 慈雲山中央球場大合唱<br />\n【港島】<br />\n維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌至西灣河海濱長廊<br />\n柴灣公園<br />\n【東涌】<br />\n東涌海濱長廊，百慕達公園<br />\n【離島】<br />\n2115 長洲東灣"},{"pid":"8fbf3f32643f626b1142e2f238e980a69616d123","tid":1565193,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"搵612<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都破產咁濟了 大家支持住！"},{"pid":"2d1352ddc945d199dd1eced7efa4de00eb602e5a","tid":1565193,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%